title: HGB BonusCast 4 - Outtakes
itunes:title: HGB Bonuscast 4 - Outtakes
description: As a special thank you to our listeners, here is BonusCast 4 featuring some outtakes from the show. We're not sure you'll think of it as much of a gift, but we pull back the curtain to reveal we aren't perfect...shocking we know! Enjoy!
